		{"id":"d854ed68411a9ff3","type":"text","text":"Book Link: https://formarse.com.ar/libros/aventuras-pdf/Juego%20de%20tronos/1.-Juego%20de%20tronos%20-%20George%20R.%20R.%20Martin.pdf\n\n\n\n|                 |      |\n| --------------- | ---- |\n| PRÓLOGO         | 11   |\n| Bran(1)         | 20   |\n| CATELYN (1)     | 28   |\n| DAENERYS (1)    | 33   |\n| EDDARD (1)      | 43   |\n| Jon (1)         | 52** |\n| CATELYN (2)<br> | 60   |\n| ARYA (1)        | 69   |\n| BRAN (2)        | 76   |\n","x":40,"y":-1420,"width":280,"height":580,"color":"1"},
